<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 14:07:17 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>加沙大规模移民和犹太人定居点：以色列立法者并不隐藏他们的愿望</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article/.premium/migration-from-gaza-and-settlement-by-jews-israeli-lawmakers-dont-hide-their-wishes/0000018c-e924-d765-ab9d-f97d6bdb0000</link><description>在一次右翼分子核心会议上，MKs 提出了诸如“在加沙地带北部，我们首先必须征服、吞并、摧毁所有房屋”之类的建议。每次有人提到加沙安置问题，都会爆发出热烈的掌声</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 13:36:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article/.premium/migration-from-gaza-and-settlement-by-jews-israeli-lawmakers-dont-hide-their-wishes/0000018c-e924-d765-ab9d-f97d6bdb0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防部长向《华尔街日报》表示：真主党知道“我们可以将[加沙]复制粘贴到贝鲁特”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article/israeli-defense-minister-to-wsj-hezbollah-knows-we-can-copy-paste-gaza-to-beirut/0000018c-e8c6-d249-a1ce-efc7f72f0000</link><description>国防部长约夫·加兰特对《华尔街日报》表示，“八万人需要能够安全返回家园”，他指的是在黎巴嫩边境附近流离失所的以色列人</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 13:08:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article/israeli-defense-minister-to-wsj-hezbollah-knows-we-can-copy-paste-gaza-to-beirut/0000018c-e8c6-d249-a1ce-efc7f72f0000</guid></item><item><title>数十名以色列人阻挡议会呼吁选举，被强行驱散，其中一人被捕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article/.premium/dozens-of-israelis-blocking-knesset-to-call-for-elections-forcibly-dispersed-one-arrested/0000018c-e8a8-d765-ab9d-f8fd78200000</link><description>集会上的一名抗议者表示，“我的兄弟被谋杀了，因为一个人为了生存而发动了一场针对国家的私人战争”，这次集会是由其成员于 10 月 7 日被杀的家庭组织的。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 11:37:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article/.premium/dozens-of-israelis-blocking-knesset-to-call-for-elections-forcibly-dispersed-one-arrested/0000018c-e8a8-d765-ab9d-f8fd78200000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在黎巴嫩边境与看不见的敌人作战</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-israeli-soldiers-fighting-an-invisible-enemy-on-the-lebanon-border/0000018c-e44c-dc46-a1ec-fefc15d70000</link><description>以色列军队和留在遥远北方的少数居民已经了解了真主党发射反坦克导弹的惯例。但他们无法习惯被搁置的生活</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 11:06:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-israeli-soldiers-fighting-an-invisible-enemy-on-the-lebanon-border/0000018c-e44c-dc46-a1ec-fefc15d70000</guid></item><item><title>加沙人可以自由地表达他们对哈马斯和 10 月 7 日袭击事件的看法吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-08/ty-article-opinion/.premium/can-gazans-freely-say-what-they-think-about-hamas-and-the-october-7-attack/0000018c-e4c0-d249-a1ce-efc59aeb0000</link><description>以色列的空袭和炮击造成的死亡和破坏规模削弱了批评或质疑哈马斯战略逻辑的意愿</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 09:58:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-08/ty-article-opinion/.premium/can-gazans-freely-say-what-they-think-about-hamas-and-the-october-7-attack/0000018c-e4c0-d249-a1ce-efc59aeb0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的支持者对他咒骂并撒谎。现在他们需要他来拯救以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article/.premium/for-months-bibi-ists-cursed-and-lied-about-barak-now-they-need-him-to-save-israel/0000018c-e59e-d249-a1ce-efdff7d40000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡的帮派在政府、媒体和街头羞辱了这位前最高法院院长。比比授予巴拉克这个角色，给了他令人印象深刻的认可</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 04:11:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article/.premium/for-months-bibi-ists-cursed-and-lied-about-barak-now-they-need-him-to-save-israel/0000018c-e59e-d249-a1ce-efdff7d40000</guid></item><item><title>拜登寻求缓和与真主党的关系，极右翼部长使以色列与美国关系紧张</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article/.premium/far-right-ministers-strain-israel-u-s-ties-as-biden-seeks-deescalation-with-hezbollah/0000018c-e5b8-d765-ab9d-f5fd40f70000</link><description>美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯自10月7日起开始第四次中东之行，拜登政府担心内塔尼亚胡将与黎巴嫩的冲突升级视为其政治生存的关键</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 04:11:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article/.premium/far-right-ministers-strain-israel-u-s-ties-as-biden-seeks-deescalation-with-hezbollah/0000018c-e5b8-d765-ab9d-f5fd40f70000</guid></item><item><title>真主党证实高级指挥官在以色列对黎巴嫩南部的袭击中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article-live/hezbollah-confirms-senior-commander-killed-in-israeli-strike-in-south-lebanon/0000018c-e702-d765-ab9d-f77fb8fe0000</link><description>真主党精锐部队高级指挥官在袭击中身亡 ■ 以色列人在以色列北部被反坦克导弹打伤 ■ 世卫组织第四次取消对加沙北部的援助 ■ 数十名抗议者在封锁议会入口后强行驱散，高呼“现在就选举” ■ 三人在以色列死亡加沙南部拉法附近的汽车遭到空袭 ■ 以色列国防军主席称战争将持续一整年</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 03:58:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article-live/hezbollah-confirms-senior-commander-killed-in-israeli-strike-in-south-lebanon/0000018c-e702-d765-ab9d-f77fb8fe0000</guid></item><item><title>迈克·彭斯不应该在以色列炸弹上签上自己的名字</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-07/ty-article/.highlight/mike-pence-shouldnt-have-signed-his-name-on-an-israeli-bomb/0000018c-e4a6-d765-ab9d-f4ffc84e0000</link><description>普通人对自己生活的任何方面都无法控制的事情应该被原谅，而强大的国家元首和决策者则不应该被原谅</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 21:58:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-07/ty-article/.highlight/mike-pence-shouldnt-have-signed-his-name-on-an-israeli-bomb/0000018c-e4a6-d765-ab9d-f4ffc84e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列边防警察向另一辆在西岸银行撞向女警察的车辆开枪，一名巴勒斯坦幼儿被流弹身亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-07/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-child-killed-by-stray-fire-from-israeli-border-police-in-w-bank-car-ramming/0000018c-e55c-db55-a39e-f7dcde820000</link><description>警方称，在耶路撒冷北部的事件中，撞倒女警察的汽车司机和车内的一名女乘客也被杀</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 20:29:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-07/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-child-killed-by-stray-fire-from-israeli-border-police-in-w-bank-car-ramming/0000018c-e55c-db55-a39e-f7dcde820000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡盟友抨击他任命前最高法院院长审理国际法院种族灭绝案的决定</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-07/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-allies-slam-his-decision-to-appoint-ex-top-court-president-to-icj-genocide-case/0000018c-e525-d765-ab9d-f57dfc9f0000</link><description>被选中的人选是前最高法院院长阿哈伦·巴拉克(Aharon Barak)，他对司法改革计划持反对态度，去年他的家门前就成为愤怒抗议的目标。一些内塔尼亚胡的政党成员谴责他被任命为国际法院司法小组成员是“错误的”，并且他们“不信任他”</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 20:09:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-07/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-allies-slam-his-decision-to-appoint-ex-top-court-president-to-icj-genocide-case/0000018c-e525-d765-ab9d-f57dfc9f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列承认真主党袭击对战略空军基地造成严重破坏</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-01-07/ty-article/israel-hezbollah-missile-strike-extensive-damage-strategic-airbase-meron/0000018c-e518-db55-a39e-f79ccc940000</link><description>真主党的导弹是向以色列北部的梅龙基地发射的。虽然铁穹系统可以拦截火箭弹，但以色列没有拦截真主党使用的反坦克导弹的系统</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 19:12:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-01-07/ty-article/israel-hezbollah-missile-strike-extensive-damage-strategic-airbase-meron/0000018c-e518-db55-a39e-f79ccc940000</guid></item><item><title>地区冲突迫在眉睫，美国国务卿布林肯抵达以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-01-07/ty-article/.premium/u-s-secretary-of-state-blinken-arriving-in-israel-as-regional-conflict-looms/0000018c-e4d7-d249-a1ce-efd78a0c0000</link><description>加沙的人道主义危机、黎巴嫩与真主党的边境紧张局势、哈马斯仍扣押的 130 多名人质——美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯周一访问以色列期间将有很多要讨论的内容</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 18:53:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-01-07/ty-article/.premium/u-s-secretary-of-state-blinken-arriving-in-israel-as-regional-conflict-looms/0000018c-e4d7-d249-a1ce-efd78a0c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列喜剧演员的加沙“旅行博客”视频引起社交媒体愤怒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-comedians-gaza-travel-blog-video-causes-social-media-outrage/0000018c-e4c5-db55-a39e-f7d585810000</link><description>喜剧演员盖伊·霍赫曼曾多次随以色列军队进入加沙地带，他在被毁坏的巴勒斯坦房屋和海滩上拍摄了一段嘲讽视频。以色列国防军表示，霍赫曼上次访问没有获得适当的授权，他们正在调查这一事件</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 18:22:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-comedians-gaza-travel-blog-video-causes-social-media-outrage/0000018c-e4c5-db55-a39e-f7d585810000</guid></item><item><title>分享一年前新闻的以色列 X 账户是对我们未来的持续警告信号</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-israeli-x-account-that-shares-news-from-a-year-ago-is-a-warning-sign-for-our-future/0000018c-e3fd-d614-a3cf-effdec5a0000</link><description>“一年前的新闻”开始发布去年的新闻，当时新冠疫情是以色列人能想象到的最可怕的事情。然后，10 月 7 日和加沙战争恰逢以色列极端主义政府成立的日子。到目前为止，该页面的关注者知道情况只会变得更糟</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 17:46:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-israeli-x-account-that-shares-news-from-a-year-ago-is-a-warning-sign-for-our-future/0000018c-e3fd-d614-a3cf-effdec5a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列任命前最高法院院长阿哈伦·巴拉克为国际法院种族灭绝案司法小组成员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-appoints-ex-top-court-president-aharon-barak-to-judge-panel-in-icj-hearing/0000018c-e4f0-db55-a39e-f7f4a4a60000</link><description>巴拉克在该案中的任命，涉及南非对以色列在加沙行动的投诉，是基于以色列作为案件当事方，除了国际法院常规的 15 名法官组成的小组之外，还有权任命一名法官</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 17:27:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-appoints-ex-top-court-president-aharon-barak-to-judge-panel-in-icj-hearing/0000018c-e4f0-db55-a39e-f7f4a4a60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列大学寻求对分享减少 10 月 7 日大屠杀帖子的学生进行更严厉的惩罚</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-07/ty-article/.premium/university-seeks-stiffer-punishment-of-student-who-shared-post-diminishing-oct-7-massacre/0000018c-e47d-db55-a39e-f7fdb8c10000</link><description>大学纪律委员会决定对她进行谴责并责令她从事社区服务，引发了校园抗议。该大学校长建议该学生“明天不要像什么事都没发生一样返回学校”，而是“在图书馆或任何你认为合适的地方”学习</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 17:00:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-07/ty-article/.premium/university-seeks-stiffer-punishment-of-student-who-shared-post-diminishing-oct-7-massacre/0000018c-e47d-db55-a39e-f7fdb8c10000</guid></item><item><title>摩托车司机因用头盔殴打驾车者被判入狱30个月</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-07/ty-article/.premium/motorcycle-driver-sentenced-to-30-months-in-prison-for-hitting-motorist-with-helmet/0000018c-e457-dc46-a1ec-feffc61b0000</link><description>根据起诉书，重罪犯“没有停止攻击”受害者，“即使受害者倒在地上”，并且“立即用头盔击打他，直到受害者倒在路上并失去知觉才停止”</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 15:40:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-07/ty-article/.premium/motorcycle-driver-sentenced-to-30-months-in-prison-for-hitting-motorist-with-helmet/0000018c-e457-dc46-a1ec-feffc61b0000</guid></item><item><title>两名加沙记者在以色列空袭中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-07/ty-article/two-gaza-journalists-killed-in-apparent-israeli-airstrike/0000018c-e41e-d614-a3cf-ec9f7a880000</link><description>据哈马斯政府媒体办公室称，哈姆扎·达杜赫和穆斯塔法·塔拉亚在拉法的汽车被袭击身亡</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 14:33:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-07/ty-article/two-gaza-journalists-killed-in-apparent-israeli-airstrike/0000018c-e41e-d614-a3cf-ec9f7a880000</guid></item><item><title>为什么以色列不能轰炸哈马斯让其屈服</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-07/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-israel-cant-bomb-hamas-into-submission/0000018c-e3ea-d614-a3cf-effb7b850000</link><description>2016年，内塔尼亚胡在议会会议厅读到一本书，书中主张通过压倒性的暴力才能赢得决定性的战争，这引起了轰动。但哈马斯和加沙的独特因素以及地区局势升级的威胁意味着以色列无法使用“投降或死亡”的最后通牒</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 13:53:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-07/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-israel-cant-bomb-hamas-into-submission/0000018c-e3ea-d614-a3cf-effb7b850000</guid></item></channel></rss>